<title>USA: AMCORE Financial names Edge as COO.</title>
<headline>AMCORE Financial names Edge as COO.</headline>
<dateline>ROCKFORD, Ill. 1997-04-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>AMCORE Financial Inc on Friday said it named Kenneth Edge as chief operating officer and executive vice president, a newly created position.</p>
<p>Edge will be responsible for all banking and non-banking subsidiaries and will report directly to President and Chief Executive Robert Mueleman.</p>
<p>Charlie Zanck will succeed Edge as group vice president for afiiliate banks at AMCORE, a bank holding company.</p>
<p>((Chicago Newsdesk (312) 408-8787))</p>
